<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٤٣٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6106">مُسْلِمٌ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2287">سَعْدٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4361">عُرْوَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a>قَالَتْ: <span class="c2">«لَمَّا مَرِضَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> الْمَرَضَ الَّذِي مَاتَ فِيهِ،<span class="c5"> جَعَلَ يَقُولُ:</span> فِي الرَّفِيقِ الْأَعْلَى.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>